snippet.title: Brazen Blaze - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
⚡️Join the Presidential Race NOW!⚡️
Meta Quest page: https://mydearest.net/meta_yt_s011
Steam page: https://mydearest.net/steam_yt_s011

📢Purchase now to get exclusive skins!📢
-RIOT MAGNAPLEX Skin
-RIOT GOLD Skin
-SKYBOLT BLOODY Skin

🤜 Join the Official Discord 🤛 
https://mydearest.net/discord_yt_launch

🔥About Brazen Blaze🔥
Brazen Blaze is a melee combat focused 3v3 action game.
There's only one goal in this game: “Strike down your opponent.” Simple, right?
Want to punch someone? Go trigger-happy? Smash a statue of someone famous?
Do everything that you’ve ever dreamed!

MyDearest, Inc.
#BrazenVR #BrazenBlaze #metaquest3 #SteamVR #UploadVR
